---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light space-y-2">
      <p>
        Born in Sokoto and raised across Sheffield and Edmonton, I'm a Nigerian‑Canadian researcher pursuing an
        MSc in Healthcare Data Science & AI at the University of Rochester.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work spans genetic risk prediction, low‑bandwidth telehealth prototypes, and psychometric fairness in youth mental‑health assessments. I've led community initiatives like the EYE Initiative and Black Youth for Social Innovation, translating research into employability curricula and advocacy.
      </p>
      <p>
        Mission: harness data and law to dismantle inequities in health and technology while empowering marginalized communities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">Focus areas</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Healthcare data science · AI safety · fairness</li>
        <li>Telehealth for low-bandwidth settings</li>
        <li>Genetic risk modeling · psychometrics</li>
        <li>Community research & policy translation</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>
